netbiodyn.ihm

Class Controller

  • java.lang.Object
    • netbiodyn.ihm.Controller

  • public class Controller
extends java.lang.Object
    Make the link between the views and the model according to the MVC pattern. - creates the views (Environment and JOGL) - controls the user inputs - creates the model (Model and Simulator) - modifies the model according to correct user inputs
    Author:
    riviere
    See Also:
    Model, Simulator, Environment, JOGL2Setup_GLJPanel, Command
